TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Shapley Value as a von Neumann-Morgenstern Utility
AU  - Roth, Alvin E.
AB  - [The Shapley value is shown to be a von Neumann-Morgenstern utility function. The concept of strategic risk is introduced, and it is shown that the Shapley value of a game equals its utility if and only if the underlying preferences are neutral to both ordinary and strategic risk.]
