TY  - JOUR
TI  - Homogeneous Programming: Saddlepoint and Perturbation Function
AU  - LeBlanc, Gérald
AB  - [This paper is concerned with the class of homogeneous programming problems. It is shown, to assure the existence of a saddlepoint for the associated Lagrangian, that some restrictions must be imposed on the degrees of homogeneity of the functions. Some properties of the perturbation function are also demonstrated.]
