TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Robustness of Some Standard Tests for Autocorrelation and Heteroskedasticity when Both Problems Are Present
AU  - Epps, Thomas W.
AU  - Epps, Mary Lee
AB  - [This paper considers (i) the robustness of the @t and Durbin-Watson bounds tests for first-order autocorrelation when disturbances in the linear regression model are heteroskedastic and (ii) the robustness of the Goldfeld-Quandt and Glejser tests for heteroskedasticity when the disturbances follow a first-order autoregressive scheme.]
